- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses the sequences of function calls executed by an application, which is related to programming languages.
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is a possibility as the paper discusses monitoring applications running in the field, which may involve distributed systems.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a possibility as the paper discusses the impact of monitoring on the quality of the user experience, which may involve security concerns.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper discusses the impact of monitoring on the performance of the monitored applications, which is related to systems and control.
